sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Redis
    participant Index
    participant Cosmos
    participant Connector
    participant Source

    Client->>Gateway: Request context
    Gateway->>Redis: Cache lookup
    alt cache hit
        Redis-->>Gateway: cached bundle
        Gateway-->>Client: return
    else cache miss
        Gateway->>Index: resolve request
        Index->>Cosmos: vector search
        Cosmos-->>Index: source pointers
        Index->>Connector: fetch source
        Connector->>Source: retrieve content
        Source-->>Connector: content
        Connector-->>Index: normalized content
        Index-->>Gateway: assembled bundle
        Gateway-->>Client: return bundle
    end